    id: "ETC|0000000000000010003187451|00|000|00434",
    content:
      '<p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">Dra Mart&iacute;n / Castellanos</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>Ingressat per FOD en pacient inmunodeprimit per trasplant renal, en probable relaci&oacute; a quist renal complicat.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>Actualment,</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>TA 139/74 mmHg (TAM 96 mmHg), FC 92 bpm, FR 18 rpm, T&ordf; 36.5&ordm;C (23h febr&iacute;cula 37.10&ordm;C), SpO2 basal 95%, glic&egrave;mia 205 mg/dl, di&uuml;resi 1700cc en les &uacute;ltimes 24h. </span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>A la nostra valoraci&oacute; pacient conscient i orientat, sense focalitats neurol&ograve;giques aparents, nega &agrave;lgies. Expressa persist&egrave;ncia d\'ast&egrave;nia per&ograve; millora de la sensaci&oacute; de mareig. Nega cl&iacute;nica respirat&ograve;ria (no tos, no dispnea, no esputs), nega cl&iacute;nica de bacteri&egrave;mia associada als pics febriculars, nega cl&iacute;nica miccional. Punt d\'inserci&oacute; de via perif&egrave;rica sense signes d\'infrecci&oacute;.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>A l\'auscultaci&oacute; presenta crepitants bibasals de predomini dret i tons card&iacute;acs r&iacute;tmics i buf panfocal grau III-IV, sense canvis respecte dies previs. No edemes a extremitats inferiors.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span><strong><u>Proves complement&agrave;ries:</u></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-</span><span><u>AS (03/02-&gt; 04/02)</u></span><span>: Hb 11.1 -&gt; 11.3 g/dl, plaquetes 253.000 -&gt; 248.000, leuc&ograve;cits 8.800 (N 77.5%) -&gt; 8.840 (N 76%), glucosa 182, Cr 1.79 - 1.96, FG 37.82, urea 90 -&gt; 101.6, perfil hep&agrave;tic normal, Na 134 -&gt; 133, K 4.15 -&gt; 4.17, ca 8.9, PCR 16.63 -&gt; 15.68, FG 33.89 ml/min/1.73m2.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-GSv (04/02): pH 7.41, pCO2 38, bic 22.5, EB -0.5, lactat 9.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-</span><span><u>Nivells de Tacrolimus (04/02)</u></span><span>: 18.3 ng/mL. (se l\'ha pr&egrave;s despr&eacute;s de l\'AS?)</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span><strong><u>Orientaci&oacute; diagn&ograve;stica:</u></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>1). </span><span><strong>Febre d\'origen desconegut en pacient inmunodeprimit per trasplant renal, en probable relaci&oacute; a quist renal complicat</strong></span><span>.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 1.14999997615814;"><span>-</span><span><u>TA</u></span><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;"><u>C abdomen (01/02)</u></span><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;">: Ronyons natius poliqu&iacute;stics amb major quantitat de l&iacute;quid lliure pararenal anterior dret respecte estudi previ i que molt probablement sigui secundari amb un o alguns quists drets complicats.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 1.14999997615814;"><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;">-No signes d\'infecci&oacute; a exploraci&oacute; f&iacute;sica.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 1.14999997615814;"><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;">-Pendent hemocultius. Comentem amb Microbiologia, s&oacute;n provisionalment negatius tot i que encara fa pocs dies que s\'estan incubant.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 1.14999997615814;"><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;">-Urocultiu: avui </span><span style="font-family: \'Arial\';font-size: 12px;color: #000000;">microbiologia informa telef&ograve;nicament com a negatiu.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;line-height: 1.14999997615814;"><span>2). </span><span><strong>Mixoma auricular </strong></span><span>pendent IQ ja comentat amb Cardiologia + doble lesi&oacute; mitral i EAo moderada. FEVE 40%.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span><strong><u>Pla:</u></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Canvis medicaci&oacute;: disminu&iuml;m tacrolimus a 1.5mg/dia. Augmentem furosemina 40mg/12h. Insulina ajustada.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Col&middot;locaci&oacute; de Midline.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Sol&middot;licitem PET-TC per identificar el rony&oacute; que presenta quist complicat de cares a un possible tractament quir&uacute;rgic futur.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Dilluns AS + nivells de tacrolimus. </span><span style="color: #FF0000;">Prendre el tacrolimus DESPR&Eacute;S d\'extreure l\'anal&iacute;tica</span><span>.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Pendent resultat de cultius, ja consultats telef&ograve;nicament a Microbiologia.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>-Control evolutiu.</span></p>',
